OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShowers, perhaps merging into
OL,6,Fmore persistent rain, will continue in
OL,7,Fthe northwest. Otherwise mostly dry
OL,8,Fand fine, with variable amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud. Easterly winds will gradually
OL,10,Fstrengthen.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith showers gradually easing but
OL,14,Flingering well into the evening.
OL,15,FFeeling cooler than of late with light
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
