OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLargely fine Sunday morning,
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells. Becoming cloudy
OL,7,Fduring the afternoon with a breezy
OL,8,Fnortheasterly wind developing. Feeling
OL,9,Fa lot cooler than of recent.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBand
OL,12,Fof rain clears south Monday morning,
OL,13,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Further
OL,14,Frain overnight and Tuesday morning,
OL,15,Fwith showers following. Wednesday
OL,16,Fbreezy with widespread heavy showers,
OL,17,Fpossibly thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
